strings: <voice_0x01000C55><se_def>China: want! We may see more. I hope there is no debate.
<voice_0x01000C56><se_def>China: I didn't do it because Marcelo asked me to. It was designed for Pastor Francisco.
<voice_0x01000C57><se_def>China: He is like a father to me. Joker... Dolmagos... I can't go on. ,
<voice_0x01000C58><se_def>China: ...I really want out of here. It's not that difficult to get invited to join, trust me.
<voice_0x01000C59><se_def>China: Do you agree with it? He said he would give me back the money if I would help him.
<voice_0x01000C5A><se_def>China: Jessica, from now on, I will protect you. I will never leave you, let me be your guardian.
<voice_0x01000C5B><se_high>Accuracy: He's a real Romeo. in your dreams!
